# Fashion, Home + Interiors Cotton Swatch Library + Dualities Expansion Pack

## 2,800 removable swatches for textiles, soft goods, and apparel, includes new Dualities Expansion Pack

Sku#:Â FHIC100C

$ 9,997.00

Add To Cart

Features 2,800 removable cotton swatches, including 175 new colors from the Dualities Expansion Pack. The Dualities Expansion Pack is divided into two palettes -- New Age pastels and monochromatic Shadows -- to reflect the complexity of our multifaceted lives. Experience the nuances of our dynamic world with this refined and accessible range that's perfectly suited for modern living.

The FHI Cotton Library + Dualities Expansion Pack is the ultimate reference tool for designers working in textiles, soft goods, and apparel, and is housed in collector's item packaging. This comprehensive seven-book series is organized by color family to make color selection easier and more efficient. Use the removable, double-layered swatches to seamlessly build and share palettes, communicate color choices, and provide a reference for designers, teams, and clients. Each cotton swatch is 5 x 5 cm and is double-layered and un-backed for accurate color visualization.

